invalid type: string "\nTitle: Find Products with Valid Serial Numbers\nDifficulty: Easy\nTopics: \nDescription:\nTable: products\n\n\n+--------------+------------+\n| Column Name  | Type       |\n+--------------+------------+\n| product_id   | int        |\n| product_name | varchar    |\n| description  | varchar    |\n+--------------+------------+\n(product_id) is the unique key for this table.\n